bilingual.source: The inner workings of the machine are quite complex.

yingyinNormal.en: Lane had a ledger. It contain the identities of his operatives, his terrorist associates, the entire inner workings of the Syndicate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱恩有一份账册，详细记录了执行人员和恐怖分子合伙人的身份，以及辛迪加内部运作情况。

yingyinNormal.en: Each cell in your body is surrounded by a cell membrane, a thick flexible layer made of fats and proteins, that surrounds and protects the inner components.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你身体里的每一个细胞都是被细胞膜所包起来。那是由脂肪和蛋白质组成的一层即厚又软的物质，包围着并保护着细胞内部。

yingyinNormal.en: It has details of your inner chamber few would know, Lord Khan.
yingyinNormal.zh: 上面有你内寝的细节标注，这个很少有人知道，大汗。

yingyinNormal.en: Multitasking sort of flies in the face of achieving inner peace, no?
yingyinNormal.zh: 就是脸上洋溢着各种表情，然后心里还能获得平静，是吧？

yingyinNormal.en: I don't mind it. I think Howie's just in touch with his inner child.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是不介意啦，我觉得霍华德只是内心有孩子气的一面。

yingyinNormal.en: That said, how could any outward change possibly affect the inner Smackle?
yingyinNormal.zh: 也就是说，外表上的改变怎么可能影响到内心里的史麦科呢？

yingyinNormal.en: I'll attempt to access everyone in his inner circle. You stay on the number.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要黑进他核心集团的每一个人，你盯紧号码。

yingyinNormal.en: No.No.No. The youth orchestra is a good thing. That shows you're a joiner-inner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不不，去青年管弦乐团是个好事儿，显示你有团体合作精神。

yingyinNormal.en: My father was a Maori. Lost him in the war. Ta Moko is a way to connect to my past. To my inner skin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我父亲是个毛利人，丧生在战场上，纹身能让我连接过去和我的内心。

yingyinNormal.en: Although when he comes to bed in his Batman pajamas, sometimes it feels like I'm touching his inner child.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过有时候，他穿着蝙蝠侠睡衣上床时，我都感觉是其实他就是个小孩。

yingyinNormal.en: Now you're gonna wanna apply this to the inner circles of your eyes and here's some words of encouragement.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在你想要把这个涂到内眼轮廓。这里有些鼓励的话。

yingyinNormal.en: I need you to place the charge on the inner door. Climb back to airlock 2 along the hull. Copy. I'm on my way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我需要你把炸弹放在内侧的门上，然后从外壳爬回2号气密舱好的，我这就过去。

yingyinNormal.en: Smackle, did you assume this outward change in your appearance would not affect your inner self? Of course it won't. I am Smackle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 史麦科，你是否同意你在外表上的改观会影响你内心的生活观念？怎么可能呢，我是史麦。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh yes. Oh and, the part about how they're always like drinking from our pool of inner power, but God forbid we should take a sip.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有，他们总是吸走我们储存的内在力量，但我们连尝一口都不准。

yingyinNormal.en: I customized the sedative to leave inner-ear function unimpaired. That way, however deep the sleep, the sleeper still feels falling. Or tipping.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我特制的镇静剂不会削弱听觉功能，无论如斯好睡 亦可感受到坠落感或者是翻倒。

yingyinNormal.en: The city expanded, into gorgeous inner city suburbs like Paddington, harbor neighborhoods like Rose Bay, and into beachside communities up and down the coast.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个城市不断发展，造就出帕丁顿等极其吸引的内城郊区、港口邻近地区玫瑰湾，并沿岸兴建了不同海滨小区。

yingyinNormal.en: See, Arnold built a version of that cognition in which the hosts heard their programming as an inner monologue, with the hopes that in time, their own voice would take over.
yingyinNormal.zh: 阿诺德创建了一份这种版本的认知接待员，可以直接听到对他们的编程，就像是内心独白，希望在将来他们自身的声音会取而代之。

examination_example.sentence: This way you make use of your emotions without losing your balance and <highlight>inner</highlight> stability.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这样你就可以在不失去平衡和内在稳定的情况下利用你的情绪。

examination_example.sentence: Rather, it changes the intensity of our <highlight>inner</highlight> experience.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 相反，它改变了我们内心体验的强度。

examination_example.sentence: New research says that those who can't seem to keep their <highlight>inner</highlight> monologues (独白) in are actually more likely to stay on task.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 新的研究表明，那些似乎无法保持内心独白的人实际上更有可能坚持工作。

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>inner</highlight> ears can collect sounds around you.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 内耳可以收集你周围的声音。

examination_example.sentence: The sounds then travel down to the middle ear, the <highlight>inner</highlight> ear and then to your brain.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然后声音传到中耳、内耳，然后传到你的大脑。

examination_example.sentence: How are dumpling wrappers made in some parts of <highlight>Inner</highlight> Mongolia?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 内蒙古部分地区的饺子皮是怎么做的？

examination_example.sentence: With or without <highlight>inner</highlight> speech, Pepper could complete a task equally well.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 无论有没有内心的言语，佩珀都能同样出色地完成任务。

examination_example.sentence: The robot's <highlight>inner</highlight> speech is also limited to the knowledge that researchers gave it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 机器人的内心语言也仅限于研究人员提供的知识。

examination_example.sentence: To be sure, Pepper confirmed the user's order, which led to further <highlight>inner</highlight> speech.
